{"pages": [{"words": {"text": ["City", "of", "Arcata", "Transportation", "Safety", "Committee", "Annual", "Report", "to", "the", "City", "Council", "Presented", "at", "the", "June", "6,", "2007", "City", "Council", "Meeting", "Committee", "Members", "Stan", "Elcock,", "Chair", "Eric", "Wennerholm,", "Vice-Chair", "Elias", "Elias", "Peggy", "Martinez", "Marguerite", "Powers", "(appointed", "August", "2006)", "Christopher", "Rall", "(appointed", "November", "2006)", "Oona", "Smith", "(through", "February", "2007)", "Staff", "Liaisons:", "R.", "Charles", "(Doby)", "Class,", "Public", "Works", "Director", "Monica", "Campbell,", "Public", "Works", "Administrative", "Assistant", "Captain", "Tom", "Chapman", "or", "Lieutenant", "Ryan", "Peterson,", "Arcata", "Police", "Department", "The", "Transportation", "Safety", "Committee", "(TSC)", "was", "recreated", "by", "the", "City", "Council", "by", "adoption", "of", "Ordinance", "No.", "1292", "effective", "6/18/99.", "The", "Powers", "and", "duties", "of", "this", "committee", "are", "to", "review", "all", "transportation", "safety", "matters", "and", "make", "recommendations", "to", "the", "Council,", "commissions,", "or", "City", "staff", "as", "appropriate.", "During", "the", "past", "year", "the", "TSC", "held", "twelve", "regular", "meetings", "on", "the", "third", "Tuesday", "of", "each", "month.", "This", "would", "equate", "to", "approximately", "237", "hours", "of", "volunteered", "time", "and", "at", "least", "58", "hours", "of", "City", "staff", "time.", "One", "of", "the", "major", "attributes", "of", "the", "TSC", "is", "the", "oral", "communications", "portion", "of", "the", "meeting", "when", "citizens", "may", "discuss", "their", "safety", "issues/concerns", "before", "the", "TSC", "and", "staff.", "Numerous", "concerns", "were", "discussed", "which", "sometimes", "lead", "to", "a", "change", "or", "a", "better", "understanding", "by", "all", "of", "the", "reason", "why", "something", "is", "the", "way", "it", "is.", "While", "most", "of", "the", "committee\u2019s", "time", "seems", "to", "surround", "the", "issues", "of", "traffic", "calming,", "bicycle", "and", "pedestrian", "safety", "issues", "and", "development", "review,", "these", "additional", "specific", "items", "were", "discussed", "and/or", "reviewed:", "Traffic", "Calming", "Projects/Priorities", "(Funding", "Priorities)", "\u2022", "Current", "Projects", "including:", "\u201cK\u201d", "Street", "Rehabilitation;", "Samoa", "Blvd.", "Gateway;", "Safe", "\u2022", "Routes", "to", "School", "Cycles", "5", "and", "7;", "Courtyards", "Phase", "II", "and", "III;", "\u201cQ\u201d", "Street", "Subdivision;", "Foster", "Avenue", "Subdivision;", "12th", "&", "\u201cO\u201d", "Streets", "(Reid", "&", "Wright);", "Downtown", "Improvements;", "\u201cG\u201d", "Street", "\u2013", "Rotary", "Park;", "Zanzi", "Major", "Subdivision", "(Giuntoli", "Lane);", "27th", "Street", "Subdivision;", "30th", "Street", "Subdivision;", "Humboldt", "Bay", "Housing", "Development", "Corporation"], "bbox": [[0.185489, 0.087152, 0.056111, 0.033552], [0.249002, 0.087152, 0.027123, 0.033552], [0.284308, 0.087152, 0.086402, 0.033552], [0.379185, 0.087152, 0.192622, 0.033552], [0.579991, 0.087152, 0.082919, 0.033552], [0.670572, 0.087152, 0.143555, 0.033552], [0.275685, 0.116241, 0.095027, 0.033552], [0.379018, 0.116241, 0.088679, 0.033552], [0.476005, 0.116241, 0.025307, 0.033552], [0.509619, 0.116241, 0.039742, 0.033552], [0.557668, 0.116241, 0.056033, 0.033552], [0.621162, 0.116241, 0.102985, 0.033552], [0.298822, 0.175559, 0.076222, 0.020212], [0.379918, 0.175559, 0.014234, 0.020212], [0.399595, 0.175559, 0.023997, 0.020212], [0.428466, 0.175559, 0.035525, 0.020212], [0.468864, 0.175559, 0.014783, 0.020212], [0.489011, 0.175559, 0.039446, 0.020212], [0.533332, 0.175559, 0.033328, 0.020212], [0.570966, 0.175559, 0.061127, 0.020212], [0.636438, 0.175559, 0.064304, 0.020212], [0.418036, 0.210408, 0.086013, 0.020212], [0.509032, 0.210408, 0.07259